  "created_file_previews": {
    "docs/ops-handoff.md": "# Office Ops Handoff\n\n## Current Status\nOffice reopening delayed from Tuesday to Thursday due to BadgeCo badge shipment slip. Ops needs a durable handoff for the next lead.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Hybrid schedule retained (no announcement until access badges confirmed)\n- Desk map to be published\n- Owner: Maya\n\n## Risks\n- BadgeCo: second missed delivery window; escalated to Jules at vendor; risk: no badges for contractors\n- Catering overrun if headcount exceeds 45 (budget: $4,800 remaining)\n- Unclear desk ownership\n- Old visitor policy still linked in onboarding draft\n\n## Owners & Next Steps\n- Ken: Budget decision needed by Friday (catering overrun risk)\n- Maya: Publish desk map after badge confirmation\n- Priya: Onboarding insert after office story is agreed (desk map, badge pickup, Wi-Fi, office norms)\n- Jules: Escalate BadgeCo delivery\n\n## Related Files\n- docs/context.md\n- finance/budget-notes.md\n- notes/leadership-meeting.txt\n- people/onboarding.md\n- risks/register.md\n- vendors/badgeco.md\n"
  },
